Overview (README)

	This directory holds the currently under development test
suite for FreeSDP.

	* torture - the main test performer

	* rfc2sdps - a Perl script that builds a file with SDP
descriptions extracted from RFCs and Internet drafts such as
draft-ietf-mmusic-offer-answer-examples. These files are used as input
to 'torture'.
